-- Marubeni to part finance Gavilon deal via bank borrowing
-- 
-- Tue May 29, 2012 5:02am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/05/29/us-gavilon-marubeni-finance-idUSBRE84S0CH20120529

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Marubeni Corp said on Tuesday it will finance part of the $3.6 billion cost of acquiring U.S. grain merchant Gavilon LLC through bank borrowing. 
 Marubeni said earlier in the day that it will buy Gavilon has debts of $2 billion. (Reporting by Miki Kayaoka; Editing by  Michael Watson )